data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home. Located minutes from Lackland Air Force Base. Lovingly kept; boasting vinyl flooring, neutral colors through-out, and an open floor plan. Large, open kitchen with modern blue cabinets and plenty of space to add a kitchen island! Primary room has a full bath with a shower/tub combo. Good sized rooms. Laundry room located in hallway. Enjoy entertaining in the big backyard with privacy wood fencing, and a covered slab patio with picnic table and a storage shed! Conveniently located near schools, shopping, with easy access to I35, and 410.
